{"title":"入冬知松柏","authors":["宋曙光"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":12,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"入冬知松柏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宋曙光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏是四季的见证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会因为夏天是花卉的节日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就羡慕那些七彩花蕾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不与万木争宠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一种花木"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有自己美丽的极致"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"置身万木丛中的松柏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不媚俗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初衷不改"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一袭四季不褪的绿色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更衬出信念的执著"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当暴风雪之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏都会重获一次养分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要根须活着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就总有绿色的希冀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能扼杀大森林的向往呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旦脱去冬衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏又会率先掀起一片绿潮"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}